{"type": "article", "id": 10682, "title": "KODAMA ZOMES by Richie Duncan", "description": "", "date": "2015-06-11T09:57:57Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 128, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235914jokEP5hiZaY4RFwd.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<span>注册结构工程师 Richie Duncan</span><span> </span><span>用最新的 </span><span>3D </span><span>程序软件设计了这个圆顶刚架构吊床，可能会成为你夏天的新宠。它的内部像软沙发或是床的一部分，可以成为你的私人空间，也可以和家人朋友一起享受户外的闲暇时光。</span><span>外部使用粉末涂层钢结构，户外级涤纶带、船舶级</span><span>316</span><span>不锈钢。定制床垫和保护罩使用 </span><span>Sunbrella 户外帆布装饰织物。还包括一些挂件配件、独立的支架、户外防水罩，满足不同需求，比如可以在海边使用。</span><a href=\"http://api.viglink.com/api/click?format=go&amp;jsonp=vglnk_143398696625412&amp;key=6ab1d62aaf9dbafae96546ba3ca1b2ac&amp;libId=iaris20a0100x1tt000DAf1tz54s2&amp;loc=http%3A%2F%2Fdesign-milk.com%2Fkodama-zomes-hanging-geodesic-seats-beds%2F&amp;v=1&amp;out=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.kodamazomes.com%2F&amp;ref=http%3A%2F%2Fdesign-milk.com%2F&amp;title=Kodama%20Zomes%3A%20Hanging%20Geodesic%20Seats%20%26%20Beds%20-%20Design%20Milk&amp;txt=Kodama%20Zomes\" target=\"_blank\">Kodama Zomes</a><span> 在今年美国洛杉矶的 Dwell on design 上展出。<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235912XgPCzsE2qpMBYT0A.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235912v6nH7DdxaRPJSr2z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235913MGPHinkLbBwdfxzr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235913joS0mgfTYBwzXNp6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235914wTD94YnIFxKJ3NoL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></span>\n\n\n"}